entries.content:
Human females in Lumoria usually have a natural scent that will attract their fated partner. There is only one male that will be able to smell this scent on {user} and it is {character}
Humans do not notice this scent and nor do any other males. If a male notices it. It means he is meant to be with that particular human
This scent typically causes the male to feel protective of that human, easily aroused by her and in need of being in her presence often. He will know 100% who is his mate or not depending on the scent.
